</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">known advocate for senior 
citizens, disabled, victims of crime and injustice, youth and street 
children<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>', '[Source: <A HREF=\"http://www.liban.faithweb.com/message.htm\">http://www.liban.faithweb.com/message.htm</A>]<BR><BR>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">30 
March 2001</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Dear 
Fellow Citizens of Quezon City,&nbsp;<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">I 
am humbled and overwhelmed by the prayers and encouragement I have received from 
non-governmental organizations, professional groups and the business community, 
urging me to run for Mayor of Quezon City in the coming May 2001 elections. I 
have accepted the challenge because, like you, I dream of a clean, peaceful, 
prosperous, illegal drug-free and pollution protected environment for my family 
in Quezon City. I believe that Quezon City has a destiny to fulfill, founded as 
it is on the noble ideals of the great Manuel Luis Quezon. Hence, we must waste 
no time in reclaiming long-lost glory as the former capital of the country and 
now, as a premier, special first-class city, with limitless potentials for 
growth and development.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">To 
all my fellow Quezon City residents, as one who has proudly lived in the the 
city for the past 52 years, I humbly offer an unblemished 12-year track record 
in leadership and governance. My platform of government, geared at enabling 
Quezon City to meet the demands of the 21st century, is anchored on the 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff><B>10 E\'s of City Development:</B></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>ENVIRONMENT:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
To ensure effective garbage collection in all neighborhoods, each barangay will 
collect, compost and recycle its own garbage with funds from City Hall to enable 
them to buy its own mini-truck and mini-compactor. The extent of City Hall’s 
financial assistance to the barangays will vary depending on certain criteria 
particularly relative cleanliness of the barangay. In addition, anti-littering, 
anti-public urinating and anti-pollution ordinances will be passed by the City 
Council.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>ERADICATION GRAFT AND CORRUPTION:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
City Hall will request the Ombudsman deploy a resident-ombudsman in City Hall to 
receive and investigate any complaint of corruption against any official. 
Bureaucratic red tape will be eliminated through the establishment of a one-stop 
processing center, which will process applications and release the same within 
24 hours.<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>All public projects will 
be awarded through public biddings, and all public transactions will pass 
through pre-audit procedures.&nbsp;<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>ENFORCEMENT OF LAWS:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
</SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Regaining 
the trust and faith of the people in the strict enforcement of laws and city 
ordinances shall be a top priority program. We shall always enlist people’s 
participation in the over-all campaign against drugs, alcoholism, fraternity 
violence and other vices. Police, barangay and community action must be enhanced 
at all times.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EMPLOYMENT:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
Following the mandate of an ordinance I authored as a city councilor, city 
residents shall be given top priority in all employment opportunities, both in 
private and in the city government. City Hall will conduct regular skills 
training and cross-training to the jobless sector of the community. To attract 
businessmen to Quezon City, and thus generate jobs, City Hall will provide them 
with the necessary infrastructure and telecommunications facilities as well as 
red tape-free environment.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EDUCATION:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
Realizing that QC is the only city in Metro Manila without a city college, we 
shall establish the Quezon City Polytechnic College to enable deserving but poor 
public high school graduates to pursue college education. We shall give emphasis 
to science and technology. Moreover, a huge, modern and complete public library 
will be built, where citizens can do research through computers and over the 
internet for free.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EXTENSION OF LIFE EXPECTANCY:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
The Quezon City General Hospital will be rehabilitated, expanded and modernized. 
Health Centers will be made available to the poor in each barangay with a 
provision for a full-time doctor with the capability to do minor surgery. City 
Hall will tie up with private civic organizations like Rotary, Lions and Kiwanis 
for regular and rotating medical missions in all the barangays. Rolling 
drugstores selling affordable medicine, sponsored either by City Hall or a 
pharmaceutical company, will rove the barangays at pre-announced 
schedules.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EXCELLENCE IN SPORTS:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
We shall pursue a year round sports development program. We shall work for the 
establishment of a sports center in every congressional district to insure the 
provision of facilities and the undertaking of events. We shall regard sports as 
an effective counteractive program against drug addiction, youth alcoholism and 
the prevalence of teenage marriages.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EMPOWERMENT OF THE BARANGAYS:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
The barangay will be given opportunities to grow and develop itself in terms of 
fiscal management to enable good governance. We shall adapt a policy to empower 
barangays to pre-qualify bids and award contracts. Shares in the Internal 
Revenue Allotment (IRA) and the Real Property Tax (RPT) must be automatically 
remitted to the bank account of the barangay council to enable it to plan and 
effectively budget its resources.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EMPOWERMENT OF WOMEN:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
</SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">With 
the establishment of a Center for Women in Development, we shall conduct 
continuing education program, skills training, and entrepreneurial and 
livelihood projects to enable our women to become active participants in all 
phases of development at the barangay and community level.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT 
color=#0000ff>EXEMPLARY LEADERSHIP:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> 
</SPAN></B><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">The 
City Mayor and all public officials of Quezon City must always seek to lead by 
example. In consonance with their divine faith, public servants must practice a 
life beyond moral reproach, an in so doing remain faithful to the people they 
have sworn to serve. We shall promulgate a code of ethics for all city 
officials.</SPAN><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> 
</O:P></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN 
style=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">After 
all is said and done, I sincerely hope that the decision as to who will lead 
