<P>
Honorable Dante V. Liban is a man of values and a family man, an exemplary father to his children Jing-Jing, Cheekee, Luzee, Kring-Kring and Carlo. He is a doting and devoted husband to his wife of 26 years, the former Marvina de Leon Reina of La Paz, Iloilo and Talipapa, Novaliches, Quezon City.
<P>
Jing-jing is currently a graduating law student at the University of the Philippines.  Cheekee after obtaining her Child Psychology degree in UP is pursuing her medical studies at the University of Massachusetts in Boston.  Kring-kring is an incoming freshman who will take up Communications Technology Management.  Luzee is a 3rd year high school student while perky Carlo is a 6th grader.
<P>
His wife, fondly called Baby by many has matched Liban’s devotion to his family with equal intensity. She gave up her post as vice president for a multinational firm in Makati City just to be able to devote her time attending to the needs of her family and her husband’s constituents. Now, Congressman and Mrs. Liban are busy devoting their lives answering the needs of the people. The successful tandem of Dante and Baby Liban only proves the truth of the dictum that behind the success of every man is a woman. Liban is also an active Catholic lay leader in Church through his membership in the Couples for Christ. He is a firm believer in the saying: \"No amount of success can ever compensate for failure in the home.\"', '', '', 'liban@pacific.net.ph', '', '932-9990; 428-5015', '0', '20010521155209', '', '', '', '', '61233', '0', 'N', '');
