<LI>Featured on the Marquis, Who\'s Who in the World since 1998 (19th Edition) and Who\'s Who of World Professionals up to the present</LI>
<LI>Legal practitioner on Taxation, Telecommunications, Broadcasting, Criminal cases and Labor cases since 1986 </LI>
<LI>Radio Broadcaster since 1983, currently doing the radio morning show on 104.3 FM Mondays and Fridays on DWBR.</LI>
