</LI></UL></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE></UL><B>
<P>6. Secretary of the Department of Agriculture</P>
<UL>
<UL></B>
<LI>After two years of implementation of the AFMA, the government managed to 
reverse the fast-declining farm productivity that had hobbled previous 
administrations. In 1999, the Philippines was able to produce 11.8 million 
metric tons of palay, the highest in history, and 4.6 million tons of corn, the 
