chaired by Mwalimu Julius Nyerere of Tanzania.&nbsp; The Commission issued a 
report in 1990 entitled <I>The Challenge of the South </I>which has since been 
translated in five languages.</FONT></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<UL>
<LI><FONT face=\"Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=1><SPAN 
